title: à-bas-le-ciel on Twitter (single-sentence monologues on veganism?)
description:
Eisel Mazard (@EiselMazard) | Twitter
https://twitter.com/eiselmazard
There's no schedule, but sometimes you can catch me on Younow (live-streaming chat-room format): https://www.younow.com/EiselMazard
Photos from my daily life are uploaded to www.oneniceapp.com (apparently to find my account you must search for my Chinese name, 马大影 …so you can copy-and-paste that, or type (in Chinese) ma-da-ying).
And, yeah, if you pay $1 per month on Patreon, you support the creation of more content on this channel: https://www.patreon.com/a_bas_le_ciel
